{"tid":626163,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 李嘉欣恭喜黎明將為人父","createTime":"2018-04-12T02:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T10:07:50.000Z","uid":48905,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a3b32866fee36a07637436af8b936d9672e6aa35","tid":626163,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:05:21.000Z","msg":"李嘉欣今日出席馬場活動時，說她也是從報章得知黎明將為人父的事，估不到對方也進入人生新階段。她指黎明一向重私隱，加上不想致電騷擾，所以沒致電及傳短訊給對方，只託其助手代為恭喜。可會跟黎明分享育嬰心得？嘉欣說︰「不敢，我的育嬰方法已過時，現在資訊發達，可以找到最新資訊。」囝囝Jayden已升小學，嘉欣每天為兒子溫習，又要照顧兩頭貓狗，十分忙碌。她表示有天抱起愛貓走到老公許晉亨面前說「我真係恭喜你呀，生了個女兒。」，囝囝立即有樣學樣。可考慮再追個女？嘉欣說︰「與兒子年齡相差太遠，順其自然吧！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/12/100515_340032c1be74a343d7c1ffb9ced877ae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F12%2F100515_340032c1be74a343d7c1ffb9ced877ae.png&h=34709ada&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"561aaeed804a623c89d35916f49d5f910341801a","tid":626163,"uid":59100,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:08:24.000Z","msg":"我真係恭喜你啊"},{"pid":"5102e719c6929990de64cab285ff437890db85bf","tid":626163,"uid":35946,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:08:37.000Z","msg":"我真係恭喜你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d73266ca3b9c5801b154f5f2259cc3baa5b99ab","tid":626163,"uid":35946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:09:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fdc57498b91c1892d16e5a07c7d45f1a830aa87","tid":626163,"uid":52881,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:09:09.000Z","msg":"嘈音POST"},{"pid":"27c779c6ed0c50e0417a45ac51c8b0fe63f043f9","tid":626163,"uid":82917,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c